Class Index

java.lang.Object
Entities.Index
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Index
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Represents an index of a course registered in STARS. Each index from the same Course can have different attributes Implements the Serializable class
